{"parentUuid":null,"isSidechain":true,"userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/anotonio.silva/antonio/mms/system","sessionId":"87960a71-f0c4-4849-b501-842c2cfd94df","version":"2.0.76","gitBranch":"main","agentId":"a64fbe9","slug":"quizzical-bouncing-marble","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"## TECH-PATTERNFLY: PatternFly v6 Design System Research\n\n**CRITICAL**: Research the DESIGN SYSTEM principles, NOT just React code.\n\n### Objective\nCreate `_migration_memory/09_patternfly.md` with comprehensive PatternFly v6 knowledge for UI migration.\n\n### Research Tasks\n\n1. **WebSearch**: \"PatternFly v6 design system 2025 documentation\"\n2. **WebFetch**: https://www.patternfly.org/get-started/design\n3. **WebFetch**: https://www.patternfly.org/design-foundations/colors\n4. **WebFetch**: https://www.patternfly.org/design-foundations/spacers\n5. **WebFetch**: https://www.patternfly.org/design-foundations/typography\n\n### Document Structure\n\n```markdown\n# PatternFly v6 Design System\n\n## Design Philosophy\n- Red Hat enterprise design principles\n- Accessibility-first approach\n- Information density vs clarity balance\n\n## Design Tokens\n### Colors\n- Primary palette (exact hex values)\n- Status colors (success, warning, danger, info)\n- Gray scale\n- Background colors\n\n### Spacing System\n- Spacing scale (4px base unit?)\n- Margin/padding conventions\n- Component spacing rules\n\n### Typography\n- Font families\n- Font sizes scale\n- Line heights\n- Font weights\n\n## Layout Patterns\n### Page Structure\n- Masthead/header\n- Sidebar navigation\n- Main content area\n- Page sections\n\n### Grid System\n- Column system\n- Breakpoints\n- Responsive patterns\n\n## Component Patterns\n### Data Visualization\n- Card patterns\n- Table patterns\n- Charts integration\n\n### Navigation\n- Primary navigation\n- Breadcrumbs\n- Tabs\n\n### Forms\n- Input patterns\n- Validation states\n- Form layout\n\n## Migration from BlueprintJS\n- Color mapping (BP Intent → PF status)\n- Component equivalents\n- Spacing adjustments needed\n\n## Code Integration\n- CSS variables usage\n- Token system in code\n- React component structure (brief)\n```\n\n### Output\nWrite complete document to `_migration_memory/09_patternfly.md`\n\nFocus on VISUAL/LAYOUT principles that will guide implementation, not just \"how to import Button\"."},"uuid":"9acce071-8a3b-4a4a-9a00-414414e4644e","timestamp":"2026-01-06T03:35:59.770Z"}
